messages.message:
*From Microsoft:*
-They are fixing the vulnerabilities we found and will find circle back if they have any questions (Approx 2 weeks)
-Beg of June when the OCR containers is GA
-Waiting for feedback on the translation services for on the Chinese to US
-For Goldman’s request on sending data out much less frequently, they are still thinking about it (Engineering wise its do-able, but from a business op’s perspective they have to see how they can approve it)
